txt.en: Deliver the crab meat, claws, and shells to Phâredar
'You will find crabs on the shoreline.'

Phâredar continues to collect the crab parts needed to make the recipes made famous by Keteph. You will need to return to the shoreline to west and south of Jax Phanâl. Collect the meat, shells, and claws from the crabs there and return them to Phâredar.
Deliver the crab meat, claws, and shells to Phâredar

Phâredar continues to collect the crab parts needed to make the recipes made famous by Keteph. You will need to return to the shoreline to west and south of Jax Phanâl. Collect the meat, shells, and claws from the crabs there and return them to Phâredar.
'Remember that the recipes call for the claws to be intact, return to me with the ingredients when you are done, and I will see you compensated well...'
'You will find crabs on the shoreline.'

Phâredar asks that you help her boss, Keteph, to maintain the supply of needed crab delicacies. With enough crap meat, Phâredar can continue delivering his signature dishes to the people of Jax Phanâl while he trains in the City of Umbar.
'Keteph's list remains the same. If you could visit the shoreline and remove the meat, shells, and claws from the crabs there we would be very appreciative. What say you?'
'I see that the cooks here are well-prepared to deliver on Keteph's recipes thanks to you.'
